    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Dolven is a narrative-driven tactical RPG where combat fuses party-based skills with poker-style card combos and deckbuilding.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In this dark fantasy world, you command a band of mercenaries against the Dungeon Master who rules each cursed dungeon. Battles unfold on a grid-based battlefield where positioning, timing, and strategy are as important as the hand of fate you hold.   </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The demo introduces you to the rich narrative and deep story, setting the stage for the journey that lies ahead.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3155820/extras/7d750e9db7c284f1543f558fedb57e52.poster.avif?t=1761866551\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3155820/extras/7d750e9db7c284f1543f558fedb57e52.webm?t=1761866551\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3155820/extras/7d750e9db7c284f1543f558fedb57e52.mp4?t=1761866551\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>A First-of-Its-Kind Combat System</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >At the heart of <i>Dolven</i> lies a unique blend of classic RPG combat and poker-inspired deckbuilding.<br>Your mercenaries wield swords, bows, and spells through traditional RPG abilities with additional buffs coming from the cards in your hand.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Form poker-style combinations called a 'Rune Combo' such as pairs, straights, and flushes to earn extra mana with which to unlock more cards, empowering your party to turn the tide of battle. Every duel is more than a clash of steel—it’s a contest against the Dungeon Master himself, with you as his opponent, that's two dungeon masters facing off.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3155820/extras/2f57d511ba3c4577661f6b4dba5adc8d.avif?t=1761866551\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3155820/extras_big/2f57d511ba3c4577661f6b4dba5adc8d.avif?t=1761866551 width=1560 height=562 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Deckbuilding &amp; Strategy</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Players construct a deck made up of two main card types:</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Mercenary Cards</strong> – Summon warriors, rogues, and mages to the battlefield.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Spell Cards</strong> – Cast magical effects, buffs, debuffs, or alter the battlefield itself.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Each card belongs to one of three archetypes—<strong>Strength (Red), Dexterity (Green), or Intelligence (Blue).</strong><br>Arrange Mercenary cards on the Pillars to form hands like pairs, flushes, or straight flushes. The in-game Compendium lists every possible combo and the rewards they bring.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >As you battle through Dolven’s maze of dungeons, you’ll customize your deck and collect gear to prepare for deadlier enemies ahead.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3155820/extras/ee540b382a088ac5093198ac62af2ee7.poster.avif?t=1761866551\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3155820/extras/ee540b382a088ac5093198ac62af2ee7.webm?t=1761866551\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3155820/extras/ee540b382a088ac5093198ac62af2ee7.mp4?t=1761866551\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>The opening cut scenes explain the narrative of Dolven in a few minutes.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3155820/extras/2fff161f77a86acf965d1b1d204e7f06.poster.avif?t=1761866551\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3155820/extras/2fff161f77a86acf965d1b1d204e7f06.webm?t=1761866551\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3155820/extras/2fff161f77a86acf965d1b1d204e7f06.mp4?t=1761866551\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3155820/extras/01a748af6edc606065d2cf6bdedcf578.poster.avif?t=1761866551\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3155820/extras/01a748af6edc606065d2cf6bdedcf578.webm?t=1761866551\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3155820/extras/01a748af6edc606065d2cf6bdedcf578.mp4?t=1761866551\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The features of the demo: </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Cut scenes to explain the story</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Grid-based battle field  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Pillars to form card hands/combos (think of it like poker)</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- 1 Dungeon</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- 2 rooms are puzzle rooms &amp; story dialogue rooms </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- No dragons YET but they form a large part of the lore! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Scallywags and zombies</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3155820/extras/539fe59d119262e223b3971287abc131.poster.avif?t=1761866551\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3155820/extras/539fe59d119262e223b3971287abc131.webm?t=1761866551\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3155820/extras/539fe59d119262e223b3971287abc131.mp4?t=1761866551\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
